      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "YUNDERUP SUN (1) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (22.87) at this track behind Moo Move in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Has a strong record out of this box with five wins and three minor placings from 11 starts. Sure to be about the mark. PRINCESS MILA (7) settled midfield in the run and boxed on to finish there when 4th (22.98) at this track. Shapes as one to consider. SHEPHERD'S WAY (8) was safely held last time finishing a 6 length fifth at this track (22.85) but back to the scene of his latest victory. Has a good record here at this journey. Comes through a solid form race last start. Key runner on best form. MR. TAYLOR (2) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.",
